=== Cross Post Blog Posts to Twitter using OAUTH - SMP Twitter Module ===
Contributors: socialmediapack
Donate Link: http://www.socialmediapack.co.uk/wordpress/social-media-pack-twitter-plugin-with-oauth/
Tags: twitter, social networking, cross posting
Requires at least: 2.0
Tested up to: 3.0.1
Stable tag: 1.3.1

Cross post your Wordpress blog posts directly to twitter using the OAUTH methed and very simple installation.

== Description ==

The Social Media Pack Twitter Module was written to cross post Blog Post's directly to Twitter using OAUTH. The plugin will automatically crop Title and Description when posting and provide a is.gd link back to the original post.

== Installation ==

1. Upload socialmediapack.zip
2. Activate the plugin
3. Go to the "Settings" menu and select "SMP - Twitter", follow the instructions
   to authorize and link your twitter account with your wordpress site

== Frequently Asked Questions ==

= Is it free? =

Yes.

= Is it simple to manage? =

Yes.

== Screenshots ==

1. After Installation, click on the Twitter button.
2. This screen will display briefly while it connects to Twitter.
3. Sign in to Twitter to confirm authorisation or if already logged in confirm.
4. Confirmation of success screen.

